<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Teresa UCB</title>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Hola, <%= @user.name %></h1>
    <p>
      Hay una persona que ha respondido a tu publicacion, la misma notificacion se te ha sido enviada a tu cuenta de Teresa.<br>

      <div class="container">
            <% @post.body.split("\n").each do |line|  %>
              <%=line%><br>
            <%end%>
      </div>


      <div class="container">
      <div ><h2><%=@sender.name%> <%=@sender.last_name%> </h2></div>
        <div class="container-body ">
         <%if !@sender.is_company?%>
          <div class="container">
          <h2>Informacion Personal</h2>
          <div class="container">
            <strong>Direccion: </strong><%=@personal_info.address%><br>
            <strong>Fecha de Nacimiento: </strong><%=@personal_info.translate_birthdate_to_string%> <br>
            <strong>Fijo: </strong><%=@personal_info.phone%><br>
            <strong>Movil: </strong><%=@personal_info.cellphone%><br>
            <strong>e-mail: </strong><%=@sender.email%><br>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="container">
          <% if @educations.size >0%>
          <h2>Formacion Academica </h2>
          <div class="container">
          <h5><% @educations.each do |education| %></h5>
                  <div>
                      <p>
                        <h5><strong><%=education.title%></strong></h5>
                        <%=education.school_name%>&nbsp;
                        <%=education.start_date.year%>&emsp; - &emsp; <%=education.end_date.year%>
                      </p>
                  </div>
              <%end%>
           <%end%>
        </div>
      </div>
      <%end%>
      </div>
        <div class="container">
          <% if @experiences.size >0%>
          <h2>Experiencia Profesional </h2>

          <div class="container">
          <h5><% @experiences.each do |experience| %></h5>
                  <div>
                      <p>
                        <h5><strong><%=experience.company_name%></strong></h5>
                        <%=experience.job_title%><br>
                        <%=experience.start_job_date%>&emsp; - &emsp;
                        <%=experience.finish_job_date%>&emsp;
                      </p>
                  </div>
              <%end%>
           <%end%>
         </div>
       </div>
      <div class="container">            
      <% if @courses.size >0%>
      <h2>Cursos y Seminarios </h2>
      <div class="container">
          <h5><% @courses.each do |course| %></h5>
                  <div>
                      <p>
                        <strong><%=course.date.year%></strong>&emsp;
                        <%=course.name%>&emsp;
                        <%=course.given%>&emsp;
                        <%=course.institution%>&emsp;
                        <%=course.workload%>&emsp; Hrs.
                      </p>
                  </div>
              <%end%>
           <%end%>
         </div>
       </div>
       <div class="container">              
       <% if @knowledges.size >0%>
           <h2> Conocimientos</h2>

           <div class="container">
          <h5><% @knowledges.each do |know| %></h5>
                  <div>
                      <p>
                        <strong><%=know.area%></strong><br>
                        <%=know.description%>
                      </p>
                  </div>
              <%end%>
           <%end%>
         </div>
       </div>
       <div class="container">
          <% if @publications.size >0%>
           <h2> Publicaciones </h2>

           <div class="container">
          <h5><% @publications.each do |pub| %></h5>
                  <div>
                      <p>
                        <strong><%=pub.publicationType%></strong><br>
                        <%=pub.date.year%>&emsp;<strong><%=pub.name%></strong><br>
                        <%=pub.location%>

                      </p>
                  </div>
              <%end%>
           <%end%>
         </div>
       </div>
       <div class="container">
          <% if @merits.size >0%>
           <h2> Meritos </h2>
           <div class="container">

          <h5><% @merits.each do |merit| %></h5>
                  <div>
                      <p>
                        <strong><%=merit.date.year%></strong>&emsp;<%=merit.name%><br>
                      </p>
                  </div>
              <%end%>
           <%end%>
         </div>
       </div>
       <div class="container">
      <% if @memberships.size >0%>
      <h2> Membresia </h2>
      <div class="container">

          <h5><% @memberships.each do |member| %></h5>
                  <div>
                      <p>
                        <strong><%=member.name%> en <%=member.organization%></strong><br>
                        desde <%=member.date.year%>&emsp;<br>
                      </p>
                  </div>
              <%end%>
           <%end%>
      </div>
      </div>
      <div class="container">
      <% if @languages.size >0%>
       <h2> Idiomas </h2>
       <div class="container">
           <h5><% @languages.each do |language| %></h5>
                   <div>
                       <p>
                         <strong><%=language.name%> Nivel:  <%=language.level%> Destreza: <%=language.skill%></strong><br>
                       </p>
                   </div>
               <%end%>
            <%end%>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>




    </p>
      Si gustas contactarte con esta persona, en el sistema estan los datos del contacto.
    <p>
      Gracias por ser parte de Teresa y esperamos saques provecho de ella.
    </p>
    </body>
</html>
